## TABLES SUPABASE NÉCESSAIRES

### Nouvelle table : lixman_conversations
```sql
id BIGSERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id),
role TEXT ('user' ou 'lixman'),
message TEXT,
health_tags TEXT[], -- ['headache', 'fatigue', 'hydration', etc.]
data_references JSONB, -- quelles données LixMan a consultées
created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()
```

### Nouvelle table : lixman_observations
```sql
id BIGSERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id),
observation TEXT,
severity TEXT ('info', 'warning', 'alert'),
category TEXT ('nutrition', 'hydration', 'activity', 'mood', 'medical'),
data_evidence JSONB, -- les données qui supportent l'observation
is_resolved BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()
```

### Nouvelle table : medibook_history
```sql
id BIGSERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id),
period_start DATE,
period_end DATE,
pdf_url TEXT,
observations_count INTEGER,
generated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()
```

